&lt;h3&gt;History&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DORAN GROUP Ltd is an organization that was established on the base of already functioning from 2007 company: Andrzej Rogulski DORAN. The partnership was founded as a response to rising demand for renewable energy sector services. Thanks to well-established market position, worked out through over six years of Andrzej Rogulski DORAN activity, we have the knowledge and experience needed to realize the most difficult tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Aim and Mission&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our goal is to constantly develop basic profiles of activity:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Processing of agro and wood biomass for pellet&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Biomass combustion technologies&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Energetic plantations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Moreover, we still liven up our offer, expanding the range of services to fully satisfy our client.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are able to implement even the most complex projects. All of this is possible by highly qualified staff and specialized companies with whom we cooperate in the implementation of new challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our mission&lt;/strong&gt; is to provide to our customers the highest quality products from the renewable energy sector so we help the environment together thus the planet. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
